"n.园艺学 【英】 园艺学(the art or science of growing flowers, fruits, vegetables, or shrubs, esp. in gardens or orchards) 【考】 tree : forestry / flower : horticulture(林学研究树木/园艺 学研究花) 【记】 horti(花园)+culture (培植)→园艺学 【同】 参考：hortitherapy( 通过种花草而治病的 园艺疗法) n. 园艺学(有关种植水果, 蔬菜, 鲜花或装饰性植物的学问或技巧) 【记】horti花园, culture(n 文化; 培植)－园艺学 【类】tree: forestry = flower: horticulture 林学研究树木 = 园艺学研究花 【记】hort- 花园 garden；horse + culture 马→田园 + 文化→园艺学；harvest收获 + culture文化→收获庄稼，植物的文化→园艺； horticulture (n.)  1670s, ""cultivation of a garden,"" fabricated from Latin hortus ""garden"" (see yard (n.1)) + cultura (see culture); probably on model of agriculture. Famously punned upon by Dorothy Parker."
